      "id": "9a437d4f_618066f7",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/policy/templates/dep-pap.yaml",
      "patchset_number": 8,
      "line": 98,
      "message": "Some containers bring war files that are opened during tomcat/jetty start. If we substitute the log config files before they start, they do not manage to deploy the war files. Therefore we allow them to start and only after we replace the logback.xml file, which is picked up dynamically.",
      "author": {
